title: Feather duster 5PCS kit with 30-100 inch telescopic extension pole, detachable bendable and reusable gap hand crevice brush for cleaning dust cobwebs on high ceiling fans lights blinds cars furniture

With a 360 degree bendable microfibre cleaning cloth head and protective soft rubber cover. Protects your furniture and ceilings from scratches. Cleaning anywhere in your home, no more climbing ladders. And it can be shortened to 30 inches when storage is required

【Easy to clean, hang and store】：The fan duster head is easy to remove and clean. After cleaning the room, simply twist the threaded connecting rod counter-clockwise to remove the microfiber head and then rinse the fiber brush in warm or low hot water. Do not dry, bleach or iron. After natural fluffing and drying, it can be reused for easy storage. With handle hole for hanging on the wall or door, or you can put the head and rod separately in a drawer. 【Quality Assurance】： Quality assurance is our top priority. If you are not completely satisfied with your manual duster kit, 100% full refund or replacement! 24 hour customer service. For any questions about the Feather Duster, please email us and we will be happy to help you.
description: Product Description Throw the ladder and make it easy! Professional Cobweb Duster Kit with Extension Pole - Get Three Duster Heads Just In The Cost Of One, What A Good Bargain. The set includes three brush heads to cover almost all your daily spider webs and dust cleaning. A simple solution to the annoying task of dusting, hard to reach areas including Fans in your home and corners near the ceiling fans. An absolute home helper. It helps you to do your chores more easily and efficiently, to meet all your needs and to clean your home. Microfibre feather duster Can be bent at will to better fit the surface of the furniture to be cleaned. Silicone cap protects furniture and walls from scratches. Reduces the fall of cleaning fibre feathers for longer use. Fluffy feathers that do not harm furniture and appliances. Chenille duster Can be bent at will to better fit the surface of the furniture to be cleaned without harming it. The upgraded cleaning bristles are more dense and effective for cleaning paper and biscuit crumbs and for lighter debris. Cleaning bristles can be removed for cleaning. Machine washable or hand washable. Crevice duster The flat, long cleaning brush with a height of only 0.9 CM cleans crevices efficiently. For blinds, furniture, under sofas, under beds, with the telescopic pole you can clean further crevices and make your cleaning task easier. The flat crevice brush has the ability to absorb dust, reducing the hassle of repeated cleaning in tight spaces and the kit comes with an extra cleaning cloth for replacement. It is soft and bendable for better handling of various cleaning scenarios. Cleaning of the brush head Microfibre feather duster, not machine washable. For chenille dusting heads and crevice brushes, remove the cloth to be cleaned and support machine washing and hand washing. Note: Do not rinse the fibre brushes in hot water. Do not tumble dry, bleach or iron. After natural drying, it can be reused.
